---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout lang="en" title="Approach" description="How working with First Up Productions actually unfolds: structured, personal, and built around your corporate communication.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black pt-32">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading mb-6">How we work together.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-light/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Clear processes, personal support, a cinematic standard, and a result that does justice to your company.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MEDIA BLOCK: Showreel -->
  <section class="relative bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="relative aspect-video bg-brand-gray overflow-hidden">
        <video src="/showreel.mp4" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="auto" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></video>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHILOSOPHIE -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Good corporate content doesn't start with the camera — it starts with understanding. What does your company want to communicate? Who do you want to reach? What is the business goal behind the project? Only once those questions are clear does the work turn into a film that not only looks professional, but actually has an effect.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our approach combines cinematic craft with a clear understanding of corporate communication. The background in directing and storytelling gives every project a stronger visual language and a more deliberate narrative — whether it's a corporate film, a recruiting video, or social media content.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROZESS DETAIL -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading text-center mb-16">From first call to finished film.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-16">

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="text-5xl font-heading text-brand-accent">01</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">First conversation & understanding</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed">We talk openly about your communication goal, your audience, and the business context. No standardised briefing form — a real conversation that builds the foundation for everything else. We listen, ask the right questions, and contribute our own ideas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="text-5xl font-heading text-brand-accent">02</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">Concept & planning</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed">Building on our conversation, we develop a concept that fits your goal — thought through in content, visuals, and logistics. No generic template, but tailored to your project and your communication goals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="text-5xl font-heading text-brand-accent">03</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">Shoot & production</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed">On the shoot day we handle everything: direction, camera, sound, light. The setup is adapted to the project — from a compact shoot to a more elaborate production with multiple camera perspectives.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[120px_1fr] gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="text-5xl font-heading text-brand-accent">04</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">Post-production & delivery</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed">Editing, color grading, sound design, format exports, and so on. The finished film takes shape in post-production. You receive the result in every format you need: website, social media, presentations, internal. Everything covered to your requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WAS SIE ERWARTEN KÖNNEN -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading text-center mb-12">What you can expect from working with us</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-black p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Clear communication</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">No agency speak, no hidden processes. You always know where we stand, and you can rely on it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-black p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">A lasting point of contact</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">You speak directly with the people executing your project. Short paths, clear communication, no account manager in between.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-black p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Reliable execution</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">Deadlines are met. Agreements hold. Surprises only happen in the film, not in the collaboration.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-black p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Thinking along strategically</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">We think beyond the brief and contribute our own ideas. Where will the content be used? Who is it for? What should it trigger? That is how we make content that actually works.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-6">Let's talk about your project.</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-light/60 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">No commitment, personal, direct. Tell us what you have in mind and we'll tell you honestly how we can help.</p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a first call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
